  1.5.1 Security function
  We are committed to providing you with a safe and reliable product and use environment, and providing high-quality and reliable services is our core goal. The information collected to realize the security function is necessary information.
  1.5.2 Device Information and Log Information
  a. In order to ensure the safe operation of software and services, we will collect your hardware model, operating system version number, international mobile device identification code, unique device identifier, network device hardware address, IP address, WLAN access point, Bluetooth, Base station, software version number, network access mode, type, status, network quality data, operation, usage, service log.
