  Please understand that with the development of our business, the functions and services provided by "KingData" may be adjusted and changed. In principle, when a new function or service is related to the function or service we currently provide, the personal information collected and used will be directly or reasonably related to the original processing purpose. In scenarios that are not directly or reasonably related to the original processing purpose, we will collect and use your personal information, and we will notify you again and obtain your consent.

